@startuml duplication_map
' Revised 2026-05-13: applied audit_23/Wave-1-fix amendments
!include dark-theme.puml
title Duplication map - status of repeated code & parallel implementations

legend top right
  |= color |= meaning |
  |<$TINT_RESOLVED>| RESOLVED |
  |<$TINT_PARTIAL>| PARTIAL |
  |<$TINT_OPEN>| OPEN |
endlegend

' ----- DUP-1: WM_DEVICECHANGE listeners merged -----
package "DUP-1  WM_DEVICECHANGE listeners" $TINT_RESOLVED {
  [DisplayEventManager\n(single owner)\nsrc/Services/DisplayEventManager.cs] as D1A
  note bottom of D1A
    One HWND owns the only DeviceNotification registration.
    Fast path: DispatcherTimer 250 ms coalescer.
    Slow path: System.Threading.Timer 1 s x 10 burst.
    App.xaml.cs only consumes events; it does not register a sink.
  end note
}

