  [MonitorService.PromoteRecovered /\nPromoteReadDegraded\neagerly MarkDDCCapable +\nfires MonitorsRefreshed] as D16B
  D16A -[#green]- D16B : Refresh now participates in\nthe same acquisition outcome flow.\nDDCRecoveryService keeps retrying\nuntil candidates clear.
}

